Source code examples from: http://zetcode.com/db/mysqlpython/

Getting started
===============

$ mysql -u root -p

mysql>CREATE DATABASE python_tutorial;
mysql>CREATE USER 'pyuser'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'yellow46';
mysql>USE python_tutorial;
mysql>GRANT ALL ON python_tutorial.* to 'pyuser'@'localhost';
mysql>FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
mysql>quit


Running the code
================

$ ./version.py
$ ./show_users.py
$ ./populate.py
$ ./fetchall.py
$ ./fetchone.py
$ ./webpy_select.py
$ ./dict_cursor.py
$ ./cursor_description.py
